#MasabaMasabaReview: There are many occasions wherein director @chink_ster could have just lost control and gone over the top with #MasabaMasaba, but she restrained the storyline convincingly. Kudos to her for coming up with a series that enlightens, motivates and entertains you!

#MasabaMasabaReview: Although #MasabaMasaba is a fictional version of events, @chink_ster along with co-writers #NandiniGupta, #AnupamaRamachandran & @clickmadness highlights @MasabaG's life after the exposure to fame and success by keeping the narrative engaging throughout.

#MasabaMasabaReview: Films/web series are nothing but reel representations of the real-life. Director @chink_ster has carved a niche for herself in making realistic yet commercial cinema (#Gippi, #Khujli). Her penchant for realistic storyline continues with #MasabaMasaba.
